data.text: @RoyaleVision a woman on the left asking herself "Who the hell is this?" 😂

@RoyaleVision Robin had worked with the 🇬🇧 Synchro Team for Olympics 2012. I love the photo where he tells her something & she has a 😮 expression! I did ask once, but he never replied.😉 BTW he was performing in Chicago in the West End every night & going to the Games as Ambassador in day.
